A MADALA robbed a bank on Monday afternoon and threw the stolen cash in the air, wishing passersby a Merry Christmas, US media reported. Colorado police confirmed an “older white man” robbed the Academy Bank in Colorado Springs after threatening tellers with an unidentified weapon and fleeing with an undisclosed amount of money. READ: WATCH: KHAYA MTHETHWA - "I HAD HUGE STRUGGLES IN MY MARRIAGE!" “He started throwing money out of the bag and then said, ‘Merry Christmas!’ witness Dion Pascale told local station KKTV 11 News. A man, identified as David Oliver (65), was bust in a nearby Starbucks after the event. – NEWS24